ygData.subject: Lookin fer fletchie kit in Grobb
ygData.msgSnippet: Me young trollie in Grobb and me new to list.  Me want to take up da fletchie so I ken make bowz and arrowz to use to kill dem froggies, but me no ken find
ygData.messageBody:
Me young trollie in Grobb and me new to list. Me want to take up da
fletchie so I ken make bowz and arrowz to use to kill dem froggies, but me
no ken find fletchie kit to start. Me find one fletchie seller in middle of
Grobb by the armur and clubb store, but he no sell da fletchie kits. Is
dere anudder fletchie seller in Grobb dat sell de fletchie kits? Me luk in
Oggok, too, but no fletchie dere at all. Enywun no where to find fletchie
kits here?

Ashuk
Tunare Server
